# fusion-features.lap

[types]
BendPositionTypes: LegacyBendPositionType | OutsideBendPositionType | InsideBendPositionType | StartEdgeBendPositionType | TangentToSideBendPositionType
BendReliefShapes: StraightBendReliefShape | TearBendReliefShape | RoundBendReliefShape
BooleanOptions: DefaultBooleanOption | TrueBooleanOption | FalseBooleanOption
BooleanTypes: DifferenceBooleanType | IntersectionBooleanType | UnionBooleanType
BossAlignmentTypes: BossAlignFlat | BossAlignStepOut | BossAlignStepIn
BossHoleExtentTypes: BossHoleThrough | BossBlindFull | BossBlindDepth
BossRibExtentTypes: RibSizeByLength | RibSizeToNext | RibSuppressed
BossRibShapeTypes: BossRibShapeNone | BossRibShapeChamfer | BossRibShapeFillet
BossShapeTypes: BossBlank | BossConstDiameter | BossConstThickness
ChamferCornerTypes: ChamferCornerType | MiterCornerType | BlendCornertype
ChamferTypes: EqualDistanceChamferType | TwoDistancesChamferType | DistanceAndAngleChamferType
ClearanceHoleFits: CloseClearanceHoleFit | NormalClearanceHoleFit | LooseClearanceHoleFit
CoilFeatureSectionPositions: InsideCoilFeatureSectionPosition | OnCenterCoilFeatureSectionPosition | OutsideCoilFeatureSectionPosition
CoilFeatureSectionTypes: CircularCoilFeatureSectionType | SquareCoilFeatureSectionType | TriangularExternalCoilFeatureSectionType | TriangularInternalCoilFeatureSectionType
CoilFeatureTypes: RevolutionsAndHeightCoilFeatureType | RevolutionsAndPitchCoilFeatureType | HeightAndPitchCoilFeatureType | SpiralCoilFeatureType
ConfigurationClearanceHoleColumns: Standard_Type_Size_ClearanceHoleColumns | Type_Size_ClearanceHoleColumns | Size_ClearanceHoleColumns
ConfigurationFeatureAspectTypes: ThreadTypeFeatureAspectType | ThreadSizeFeatureAspectType | ThreadDesignationFeatureAspectType | ThreadClassFeatureAspectType | ThreadModeledFeatureAspectType | ThreadFullLengthFeatureAspectType | ThreadIsRightHandedFeatureAspectType | JointFlipFeatureAspectType | JointSnapOneFeatureAspectType | JointSnapTwoFeatureAspectType | ClearanceHoleStandardFeatureAspectType | ClearanceHoleTypeFeatureAspectType | ClearanceHoleSizeFeatureAspectType | ClearanceHoleFitFeatureAspectType
ConfigurationThreadColumns: ThreadType_Size_Designation_ClassColumns | ThreadSize_Designation_ClassColumns | ThreadDesignation_ClassColumns | ThreadClassColumns | TaperedThreadType_Size_DesignationColumns | TaperedSize_DesignationColumns | TaperedDesignationColumns
CornerBendTransitionTypes: SmoothCornerBendTransitionType | StraightLineCornerBendTransitionType | TrimToBendCornerBendTransitionType
CornerClosureFeatureDefinitionTypes: UndefinedCornerClosureFeatureDefinitionType | TwoBendCornerClosureFeatureDefinitionType | ThreeBendCornerClosureFeatureDefinitionType
CornerThreeBendReliefShapeTypes: NoReplacementCornerThreeBendReliefShapeType | IntersectionCornerThreeBendReliefShapeType | FullRoundCornerThreeBendReliefShapeType | RoundWithRadiusCornerThreeBendReliefShapeType
CornerTwoBendReliefPlacementTypes: TangentCornerTwoBendReliefPlacementType | IntersectionCornerTwoBendReliefPlacementType | VertexCornerTwoBendReliefPlacementType
CornerTwoBendReliefShapeTypes: RoundCornerTwoBendReliefShapeType | SquareCornerTwoBendReliefShapeType | TearCornerTwoBendReliefShapeType | TrimToBendCornerTwoBendReliefShapeType | LinearWeldCornerTwoBendReliefShapeType | ArcWeldCornerTwoBendReliefShapeType | LaserWeldCornerTwoBendReliefShapeType
ExtentDirections: PositiveExtentDirection | NegativeExtentDirection | SymmetricExtentDirection
FeatureExtentTypes: OneSideFeatureExtentType | TwoSidesFeatureExtentType | SymmetricFeatureExtentType
FilletFeatureTypes: FilletFeatureType | RuleFilletFeatureType | FullRoundFilletFeatureType
HemFeatureDefinitionTypes: UndefinedHemFeatureDefinitionType | FlatHemFeatureDefinitionType | OpenHemFeatureDefinitionType | RolledHemFeatureDefinitionType | TeardropHemFeatureDefinitionType | RopeHemFeatureDefinitionType | DoubleHemFeatureDefinitionType
HoleEdgePositions: EdgeStartPointPosition | EdgeMidPointPosition | EdgeEndPointPosition
HoleSegmentType: HoleSegmentTypeCylinder | HoleSegmentTypeCone | HoleSegmentTypeFlat | HoleSegmentTypeTorus
HoleTapTypes: SimpleHoleTapType | ClearanceHoleTapType | TappedHoleTapType | TaperTappedHoleTapType
HoleTypes: SimpleHoleType | CounterboreHoleType | CountersinkHoleType
LineStylePatterns: continuousLineStylePattern | centerLineStylePattern | dashedLineStylePattern | dotLineStylePattern | hiddenLineStylePattern | phantomLineStylePattern | tracksLineStylePattern | zigzagLineStylePattern
LoftEdgeAlignments: FreeEdgesLoftEdgeAlignment | AlignEdgesLoftEdgeAlignment | AlignToSurfaceLoftEdgeAlignment
LoftRailEdgeConditions: G0LoftRailEdgeCondition | G1LoftRailEdgeCondition | G2LoftRailEdgeCondition
LoopTypes: AllLoops | OnlyOutsideLoops | OnlyInsideLoops
OffsetCornerTypes: CircularOffsetCornerType | LinearOffsetCornerType | ExtendedOffsetCornerType
PatternComputeOptions: OptimizedPatternCompute | IdenticalPatternCompute | AdjustPatternCompute
PatternDistanceType: ExtentPatternDistanceType | SpacingPatternDistanceType
PatternEntityTypes: FacesPatternType | FeaturesPatternType | BodiesPatternType | OccurrencesPatternType
PipeSectionTypes: CircularPipeSectionType | SquarePipeSectionType | TriangularPipeSectionType
RipFeatureDefinitionTypes: UndefinedRipFeatureDefinitionType | FaceRipFeatureDefinitionType | AlongEdgeRipFeatureDefinitionType | BetweenPointsRipFeatureDefinitionType
RuleFilletRuleTypes: AllEdgesRuleFilletRuleType | BetweenFacesOrFeaturesRuleFilletRuleType
RuleFilletTopologyTypes: RoundsAndFilletsRuleFilletTopologyType | RoundsOnlyRuleFilletTopologyType | FilletsOnlyRuleFilletTopologyType
RuledSurfaceCornerTypes: RoundedRuledSurfaceCornerType | MiteredRuledSurfaceCornerType
RuledSurfaceTypes: TangentRuledSurfaceType | NormalRuledSurfaceType | DirectionRuledSurfaceType
ShellTypes: SharpOffsetShellType | RoundedOffsetShellType
SideTypes: AlwaysOutsideSideType | AlwaysInsideSideType | StartOutsideSideType | StartInsideSideType
SilhouetteSplitOperations: SilhouetteSplitFacesOnlyOperation | SilhouetteSplitShelledBodyOperation | SilhouetteSplitSolidBodyOperation
SplitFaceSplitTypes: surfaceIntersectionSplitType | alongVectorSplitType | closestPointSplitType
SplitSupportTypes: SolidOpenMergedSplitSupportType | SolidOpenSeparateSplitSupportType
SweepExtentTypes: PerpendicularToPathExtentType | FullExtentsExtentType
SweepOrientationTypes: ParallelOrientationType | PerpendicularOrientationType
SweepProfileScalingOptions: SweepProfileScaleOption | SweepProfileStretchOption | SweepProfileNoScalingOption
SweepSolidOrientationTypes: PerpendicularSolidOrientationType | RigidSolidOrientationType | AlignedSolidOrientationType
ThickenTypes: SharpThickenType | RoundedThickenType
ThreadLocations: HighEndThreadLocation | LowEndThreadLocation
ThreeBendReliefShapes: NoReplacementThreeBendReliefShape | IntersectionThreeBendReliefShape | FullRoundThreeBendReliefShape | RoundWithRadiusThreeBendReliefShape
TwoBendReliefPlacements: NoTwoBendReliefPlacement | IntersectionTwoBendReliefPlacement | TangentTwoBendReliefPlacement | VertexTwoBendReliefPlacement
TwoBendReliefShapes: RoundTwoBendReliefShape | SquareTwoBendReliefShape | TearTwoBendReliefShape | TrimToBendTwoBendReliefShape | LinearWeldTwoBendReliefShape | ArcWeldTwoBendReliefShape | LaserWeldTwoBendReliefShape
ViewCorners: upperLeftViewCorner | upperRightViewCorner | lowerLeftViewCorner | lowerRightViewCorner

